com.ibm.jaggr.core.modulebuilder

Class ModuleBuild

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.jaggr.core.modulebuilder.ModuleBuild

  • public final class ModuleBuild
extends Object
    Result wrapper class for built content. Instances of this object are returned by IModuleBuilder.build(String, IResource, HttpServletRequest, List).
